column5: looks like a great trip!  cheers!
Thanks for the report, glad ya had some good fishing...
Great Report. Looks like you caught a lot of fish and different species. Those bowfin(Dogfish) really put up a great fight! Thanks for sharing.
Beauty report with some nice bass! Congrats on Grandma's big birthday 100th, cause for a big party for sure.  Cheers, 1leg
Nice catches, you wear "thebassfisher" title with merit.  Congrats to your grandma's 100th, amazing.
